<A>__{puff testifies.}
<C>__{puff}
<D>__{i saw it, gentlemen. i saw the whole sweaty, passionate, ugly, beautiful act, and to use the vernacular, i wanted me some of that.}
<A>__{the congressmen laugh appreciatively. the laughter is a little too enthusiastic and goes on a little too long. it stops abruptly.}
<C>__{puff}
<D>__{and i think i understood from that moment, that in order to get some, i would have to do what they said. in order to experience this primal, basic, animal thing, i would first have to become a civilized, prissy, uptight human. i would have to become nathan.}
<A>__{the congressmen nod sadly, in recognition of this reality.}
